    %h2 Do more with your data
    %p Your data is always changing -- imagine being able to react every time your data changed. Debezium makes this easy, without having to change your apps that modify the data. Debezium continuously monitors your databases and lets any of your applications stream every row-level change in the same order they were committed to the database. Use the event streams to purge a cache, update search indexes, generate derived views and data, keep other data sources in sync, and much more. In fact, pull that functionality out of your app and into separate services.
