    %h2 Simplify your apps
    %p Since Debezium can monitor your data, why have your applications update the database <em>and</em> update search indexes <em>and</em> send notifications <em>and</em> publish messages? Doing that correctly -- even when things go wrong -- is really tough, and if you get it wrong the data in those system may be inconsistent. Keep things simple, and move that extra functionality into separate services that use Debezium.
